  <section id="reveal" class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-title">PAA Glyph Calculator</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Enter your birthdate and full birth name. The free reading gives recognition: the core sequence, the visible name-form, and the underlying engine. The full reading shows where the sequence breaks, how it repeats, and how to correct it.</p>
    <div class="glass calc-panel">
      <div class="calc-grid">
        <div>
